<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id0da24399-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0" identifier="/us/usc/t52/s21072"><num value="21072">§ 21072.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out the provisions of this part $200,000 for fiscal year 2003 and such sums as may be necessary for each of the 6 succeeding fiscal years.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id0da2439a-2931-11f1-afae-ea39e71ac6b0">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/252/tII/s296">Pub. L. 107–252, title II, § 296</ref>, <date date="2002-10-29">Oct. 29, 2002</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/116/1704">116 Stat. 1704</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
